posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'HURRY our rent-restricted apartments are going fast!', 'Submit your application paperwork quickly and easily today to reserve your new home.', 'With incredible space, luxury amenities, and a perfect location in Uptown’s vibrant neighborhood, Buzza Lofts offers the ideal place to make your home.', 'The beautiful 1 & 2 bedroom homes provide walk-in closets, open floorplans, stainless steel appliances, and an in-home washer and dryer.', 'Residents enjoy the modern fitness center, rooftop terrace, and on-site parking.', 'Gas, water, sewer, and trash removal are included in rent.', 'Visit today to learn more!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Controlled Entry Access Into Building', '- Professional & Courteous On-Site Management Team', '- Serene Rooftop Terrace With Incredible Downtown Views', '- Eco-Conscious Lighting, Heating & Water Flow Systems', '- Walk-In Closets, Just In-Case You Decide To Go On A Boutique Shopping Spree!', '- Water, Sewer & Trash Removal Services', 'Included', '- Beautiful, 42"-Inch Maple Cabinetry Provides A Clean & Finished Look To A Stainless Kitchen Design', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Buzza Lofts participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 12:00PM-5:00PM', 'Call today to learn more about our community:', 'show contact info', 'Buzza Lofts of Uptown', '1006 West Lake Street', 'Minneapolis, MN, 55408', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', '32rPd6V0wh']
